data.description:
Odaily Planet Daily News CryptoSlam data shows that in March, NFT sales on both the Ethereum and Bitcoin chains hit a new low for the year, including: 
1. NFT sales on the Ethereum chain reached approximately US$125 million, and the on-chain transaction volume was approximately 581,000 (including approximately 95,000 independent buyer addresses and approximately 70,000 independent seller addresses); 
2. NFT sales on the Bitcoin chain reached approximately US$88.97 million, and the on-chain transaction volume was approximately 176,000 (including approximately 45,000 independent buyer addresses and approximately 32,000 independent seller addresses).
